name: Reversible Signature Short Hooded Wrap Coat
shortDescription: The House’s signature short wrap coat is crafted from cosy double-face wool-silk in a versatile colourway, which reverses to reveal a graphic jacquard of the Monogram motif. Cut in an enveloping hooded silhouette, the front opening is highlighted with contrasting piping, while a casual self-tie belt accentuates the waistline and two side pockets complete the look.

name: Reversible Signature Hooded Wrap Coat
shortDescription: The House’s iconic wrap coat is crafted from sumptuous double face wool-silk in a long, enveloping silhouette complete with a generous hood and a coordinating belt to add definition to the waistline. It can be reversed to reveal a delicate jacquard of the Flight Mode capsule’s signature Mahina Monogram motif.

name: Reversible Signature Hooded Wrap Coat
shortDescription: A staple of the Flight Mode capsule, this long hooded wrap coat is crafted from plush double face wool-silk that can be reversed to reveal a delicate all-over Mahina Monogram motif. The front opening and side pockets are trimmed with tonal leather for an elevated finish, while a tone-on-tone belt adds definition to the enveloping silhouette.
detailedDescription:
• Main material: 99% wool, 1% silk
  • Natural Beige
  • Made in Italy

name: Reversible Signature Short Hooded Wrap Coat
shortDescription: The House’s iconic reversible short wrap coat is crafted from plush double-face wool-silk in an enveloping hooded silhouette for cosy yet elegant cold weather wear. In a fresh seasonal colourway, one side is signed all over with a Monogram motif. A coordinating belt adds definition to the waistline and two side pockets complete the look.

name: Lapel Collar Wrap Coat
shortDescription: This elegant coat is crafted from a warm double-face wool-silk blend in an enveloping wrap shape, which is cinched at the waist with a coordinating self-tie belt. A lapel collar introduces a structured detail to the ample silhouette while revealing a glimpse of the Monogram jacquard that signs the inside.

name: Double Face Open-Arm Jacket
shortDescription: This zip-up jacket is a sporty House staple in a contemporary open-arm silhouette. It is cut from a cosy double face wool-silk blend, which is signed on the inside with a tonal Monogram motif. The hood is trimmed with sleek leather drawstrings, while two practical pockets complete the look.

name: Diamond Ripstop Puffer Gilet
shortDescription: When styled as part of a full skiwear silhouette, this puffer gilet is a sleek yet cosy mid-layer. It is cut from ultra-lightweight waterproof nylon ripstop fabric, which is padded with feathers and finished with a quilted diamond motif. A high neckline and a coated technical zip keep out the cold, while fastened pockets add a practical detail. It is signed with a seasonal LV snowflake print on the chest.

name: Drawstring Detail Technical Puffer Gilet
shortDescription: This boxy zip-up puffer gilet is cut from ultra-lightweight nylon in a chic, glossy finish, signed with a seasonal LV snowflake print on the chest and a graphic Monogram motif on the inside. It is padded with a combination of down and feathers and finished with seamless bonding and technical topstitching to keep out the cold on the slopes. Both the cosy high neckline and arm holes can be cinched with drawstrings to emphasise the warmth.

name: Monogram Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This nylon puffer jacket is discreetly signed all over with a tone-on-tone Monogram jacquard. Cut in a modern boxy shape, feather padding emphasises the warmth and volume, while a covered front zip, ribbed cuffs and a high neckline keep out the cold. It is complete with fastened side pockets and a practical removable hood.

name: Monogram Accent Pillow Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This streetwear-forward puffer jacket takes its design cues from the House’s iconic Pillow boots. Cut from recycled nylon, the voluminous silhouette is padded with a combination of goose down and wadding for warmth and comfort. A standing collar keeps out the cold, while Monogram accents complete the clothing look with an iconic signature.
detailedDescription:
• Length: 69 cm/27.2 inches
  • Main material: 100% polyamide
  • Optic White
  • Regular fit
  • Made in Italy

name: Long-Sleeved Pillow Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This is a chic, sporty long-sleeved puffer jacket inspired by the Spring-Summer 2021 Collection’s instantly iconic Pillow Boots. It is cut from quilted nylon ripstop with a Monogram lining that can be glimpsed inside the ample hood, with coordinating Monogram canvas fastenings. This clothing piece is padded with genuine feathers for a snug feel, amped up by elasticated cuffs to keep out the cold.

name: Monogram Jacquard Knit Jacket
shortDescription: This jacket is spun from a soft silk-blend knit featuring the iconic Monogram motif as a graphic jacquard with contrasting plain black shoulders. The silhouette is long and oversized for a cosy, enveloping fit, complete with an ample hood, elasticated cuffs and a drawstring hem. This clothing piece is finished with an exposed golden front zip and two practical flap pockets.

  • Main material: 56% silk, 42% polyamide, 2% elastane
  • Black/Brown
  • Made in Italy

This clothing piece is complete with refined tone-on-tone leather piping and two practical pockets.

name: Diamond Ripstop Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This cosy hooded puffer jacket forms the mid-layer of this season’s technical ski silhouette. It is crafted from ultra-lightweight waterproof nylon ripstop fabric and quilted in a chic diamond pattern with a subtle half Monogram Flower motif on the back. Feather padding underscores the warmth, while a coated front zip, elasticated cuffs and fastened pockets emphasise the practicality. An LV snowflake adds a graphic signature to the chest.

name: Cropped Monogram Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This puffer jacket is a chic everyday essential in a cropped shape, made from nylon in a subtle all-over Monogram motif. Feather padding introduces warmth and volume, while a shirt collar adds structure to the silhouette. Monogram canvas buttons and an LV patch on the left sleeve complete the clothing look with a final signature touch.

name: Cropped Monogram Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This puffer jacket is a chic everyday essential in a cropped shape, made from nylon in a subtle all-over Monogram motif. Feather padding introduces warmth and volume, while a shirt collar adds structure to the silhouette. Monogram canvas buttons and an LV patch on the left sleeve complete the clothing look with a final signature touch.

name: Monogram Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This nylon puffer jacket is discreetly signed all over with a tone-on-tone Monogram jacquard. Cut in a modern boxy shape, feather padding emphasises the warmth and volume, while a covered front zip, ribbed cuffs and a high neckline keep out the cold. name: Denim Print Cropped Puffer Jacket
shortDescription: This puffer jacket has been playfully reimagined in soft peach-effect cotton featuring a trompe l’oeil denim print. The chic cropped shape is padded with feathers for elevated warmth and volume, while the cuffs, waist and high neckline are finished with soft ribbing for a snug fit. It fastens with an exposed zip signed with a Monogram canvas pull.

• Main material: 88% cotton, 9% polyamide, 3% elastane
  • Strong Blue
  • Made in Italy

name: Ombré Monogram Fleece Jacket
shortDescription: This cosy jacket has a modern, graphic look in fuzzy fleece featuring a print of this season’s ombré Monogram motif, which is offset by contrasting inserts of peach-effect cotton. The cuffs and high neckline can be folded over and cinched with drawstrings for versatile styling. It is complete with three practical pockets and a sporty mesh lining.
detailedDescription:
• Main material: 67% polyester, 29% wool, 2% cotton, 2% polyamide
  • Black
  • Made in France

name: Monogram Teddy Peplum Gilet
shortDescription: This cosy gilet is crafted from soft wool-blend teddy fleece in a graphic all-over print of the iconic Monogram motif, while the ample drawstring hood strikes a sporty contrast in nylon twill. The boxy cut can be cinched at the waist to form a chic peplum silhouette. It is complete with golden hardware and classic Monogram canvas accents.
